d','closed','','191-revision-v1','','','2020-07-28 07:31:27','2020-07-28 07:31:27','',191,'http://188.166.160.223/american/191-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(217,1,'2020-07-28 07:32:50','2020-07-28 07:32:50',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','217','','','2020-07-29 09:59:54','2020-07-29 09:59:54','',0,'http://188.166.160.223/american/?p=217',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(218,1,'2020-07-28 07:32:50','2020-07-28 07:32:50',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','218','','','2020-07-29 09:59:54','2020-07-29 09:59:54','',0,'http://188.166.160.223/american/?p=218',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(219,1,'2020-07-28 07:36:12','2020-07-28 07:36:12','[vc_section el_class=\"who-we-are-sec\"][vc_row el_class=\"container align-center\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1595847985841{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1595921740400{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}\"]The American Hospitality Institute is the only organization representing all stakeholders in the US hospitality industry including hotels, resorts, restaurants, casinos, spas, bed and breakfasts, peer-to-peer lodging, cruise ships, theme parks, hospitality schools, hospitality students, hotel management companies, REITS, airlines, event planners, transportation companies, entertainment companies, and industry vendors and partners.\r\n\r\nAHI is partnered with its sister organization, the International Hospitality Institute (IHI). True to their charter, AHI and AHI are committed to fostering excellence in the hospitality industry. Toward that goal, IHI and AHI launched the <strong>Julian Star</strong> Award to recognize excellence in the hospitality industry.\r\n\r\nThe <strong>Julian Star</strong> is awarded to hospitality establishments and hospitality practitioners who demonstrate exceptional customer service. Less than 1% of nominees will receive the award yearly. Covering all segments of the global hospitality industry, the 